---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Expo | PDAS 2026">
  <section class="bg-[#020617] pt-4 pb-24 px-4 md:px-8 border-b border-slate-800">
    <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto">
      
      <!-- DATA HEADER -->
      <div class="border-b border-slate-800 pb-8 mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
          <span class="relative w-2.5 h-2.5 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="absolute inset-0 bg-sky-400 rounded-full animate-ping opacity-60"></span>
            <span class="relative w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-sky-400 rounded-full block"></span>
          </span>
          <p class="text-[11px] uppercase font-mono tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-400">
            SYS.DIR // SHOWCASE // EXPO
          </p>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white uppercase tracking-tighter">
          Expo
        </h1>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
        
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-10">
          
          <div class="text-slate-400 text-lg leading-relaxed space-y-6">
            <p>
              The PDAS Expo is more than a exhibition, it is a carefully planned platform built to showcase India's growing defence capabilities to the world, with a special focus on unlocking the immense potential of the Southern Peninsula. The southern states of India hold a powerful combination of industrial strength, technical talent, and manufacturing capacity that is ready to make a significant mark on the global defence landscape.
            </p>
            <p>
              This Expo serves as the ideal stage to bring together the best defence-focused companies, innovators, and manufacturers from across South India — giving them a unified platform to present their capabilities, connect with global buyers, and step confidently into international defence markets. Soldiers, government buyers, and defence planners can explore a wide range of systems and solutions being developed right here in the South, ready to be taken to the next level.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="border-t border-slate-800 pt-10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white uppercase mb-4 tracking-tight">The Legacy & Future Pavilion</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
              The Legacy & Future Pavilion brings together the region's strong industrial base in areas such as armored vehicle manufacturing, high-precision aerospace components, and heavy-duty powertrains — showing the world the kind of production capacity and expertise that Southern India brings to the table.
            </p>
            
            <div class="bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 p-6 mb-6 rounded-lg">
              <h3 class="text-sky-400 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">The Deep-Tech Hangar</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                Dedicated to showcasing cutting-edge innovations emerging from southern India that are shaping the future battlefield from AI-powered surveillance and reconnaissance systems to quantum-encrypted communication tools and electronic warfare platforms being developed within the Tamil Nadu corridor and across the wider southern region.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
              Visitors do not just view these technologies on a display stand — they can watch live demonstrations of drones in flight, autonomous robots in action, and systems being tested in simulated battlefield environments.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="border-t border-slate-800 pt-10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white uppercase mb-4 tracking-tight">The Indigenisation Intelligence Factor</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed border-l-2 border-sky-400 pl-6 mb-4">
              Every product showcased is clearly tagged with its verified "Make in India" percentage, offering full transparency into how much of the product is built locally and the long-term supply chain strength it carries.
            </p>
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
              With southern companies leading the way in local content and self-reliant production, this is a powerful signal to the global market that India — and in particular its southern industrial belt — is not just a buyer of defence technology, but a capable, reliable, and self-sufficient producer.
            </p>
          </div>

        </div>

        <!-- VISUAL DATA PANELS -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-5 space-y-6">
           <div class="border border-slate-800 bg-[#020617] rounded-lg p-2 shadow-[0_0_60px_-15px_rgba(56,189,248,0.05)] transition-all duration-500 hover:border-sky-400/30">
             <img src="/images/hall/pdas-exhibitor1.jpg" alt="Expo Floor" class="w-full h-auto object-cover rounded-md grayscale opacity-70 mix-blend-luminosity hover:grayscale-0 hover:opacity-100 hover:mix-blend-normal transition-all duration-500" />
             <div class="p-3 border-t border-slate-800 mt-2 flex items-center justify-between">
               <p class="text-[10px] font-mono text-slate-500 uppercase">FIG. 01 // EXPO FLOOR // OVERVIEW</p>
               <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-sky-400 rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
             </div>
           </div>

           <div class="border border-slate-800 bg-[#020617] rounded-lg p-2 shadow-[0_0_60px_-15px_rgba(56,189,248,0.05)] transition-all duration-500 hover:border-sky-400/30">
             <img src="/images/hall/sponsorship-opportunities.jpg" alt="Expo Tech Showcase" class="w-full h-auto object-cover rounded-md grayscale opacity-70 mix-blend-luminosity hover:grayscale-0 hover:opacity-100 hover:mix-blend-normal transition-all duration-500" />
             <div class="p-3 border-t border-slate-800 mt-2 flex items-center justify-between">
               <p class="text-[10px] font-mono text-slate-500 uppercase">FIG. 02 // EXPO HARDWARE // TACTICAL</p>
               <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-slate-600 rounded-full"></div>
             </div>
           </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
